store_address: 18 N Dollins Ave, Orlando, FL 32805, USA
menu_items: Experience the most famous “everyday meal” of Puerto Rico. Our delicious blend of tender and juicy “bistec encebollado” (steak and Onions), savory beans, perfectly cooked white rice, and a crisp green salad with two crispy tostones to round out this mouthwatering dish.

Indulge in the explosion of flavors that the Combo Alcapurria offers, with aromatic rice and gandules (pigeon peas), a refreshing green salad, and the crispy goodness of a tostada (toast) with garlic butter, all perfectly complemented by a delicious alcapurria (Green Banana and Taro root fritter)

Take your taste buds on an adventure with the Combo Relleno, complete with aromatic rice and gandule, a crisp green salad, a tostada with garlic butter, and two delicious and savory rellenos that will keep you coming back for more.

Savor the traditional flavors of Puerto Rican holiday’s with the Combo Pastel that comes with aromatic rice and gandules (pigeon peas), a fresh green salad, a tostada with garlic butter, and a scrumptious packed-potato pastel (tamale) that is sure to leave your taste buds longing for more.

Sink your teeth into the Maui's Burger (Classic) that boasts succulent impossible meat in a delicious potato and pineapple bun! American cheese, fresh lettuce, ripe tomato, crispy cucumbers, caramelized onions, and a perfect blend of mayo and ketchup that is sure to satisfy any burger lover's cravings.

Elevate the Maui's Burger (Classic) experience by savoring simply more of everything, from double the impossible meat to double the American cheese and mayo-ketchup sauce, all nestled in a delicious potato and pineapple soft, freshly baked bun.

For the ultimate Maui Burger experience, try the Triple Maui's, which comes with three succulent impossible meat patties in a delicious potato and pineapple bun! American cheese, fresh lettuce, ripe tomato, crispy cucumbers, caramelized onions, and an irresistible mayo-ketchup sauce.

Take on a kingly challenge with the King Maui's, which boasts a whopping four impossible meat patties in a delicious potato and pineapple bun! American cheese, fresh lettuce, ripe tomato, crispy cucumbers, caramelized onions, and a perfect blend of mayo and ketchup.

Crunchy, flavorful Pollo strips meet gooey Cheddar and Mozzarella cheeses, fresh pico de gallo, creamy avocado, crispy lettuce, and a spicy salsa and mayo ketchup combo all wrapped up in a warm, fluffy tortilla. Indulge in our Wrap de Pollo today!

The Philly Cheesesteak Sandwich is a mouthwatering classic, stacked high with tender grilled beef, sweet green peppers and onions, and melted Monterrey Jack cheese, all topped off with a creamy mayo blend. Indulge in our delicious Philly Cheesesteak Sandwich today!

Sink your teeth into our juicy Sandwich de Bistec, featuring tender steak, crispy onion, fresh lettuce and tomato slices, crunchy potato sticks, and a zesty mayo-ketchup sauce. It's a sandwich worth savoring!

Enjoy our HP Chicken Sandwich! Our HP custom bread is infused with tangy pineapple. An explosion of flavors with gooey Swiss cheese, crispy lettuce, juicy tomato slices, and a spicy slaw and mayo sauce, this sandwich is sure to pack a punch

Our Buffalo Sandwich is a crispy chicken lover's dream, with tender, breaded chicken smothered in melty Swiss cheese, crispy bacon, savory onion rings, tangy BBQ sauce, and creamy mayo. It's the perfect combination of flavors and crunch!
Sink your teeth into our Slider Criollo, featuring savory Impossible meat smothered in melted Queso Cheddar, mashed maduro, caramelized onions, and tangy BBQ sauce. 3 Sliders Included!

Our Quesadillas offer a range of scrumptious fillings including tender Pollo (chicken) or juicy Steak, and rich, ooey-gooey Cheddar cheese, all served with a side of sour cream, fresh pico de gallo and creamy avocado. It's the perfect combination of your favorite Latin-inspired flavors!

Allergic to Seafood? Worry No more! 
Try our HP (Hecho de Plantas = plant based) take on a Latin Classic "CARRUCHO" It's a Conch Shellfish Salad with tasty Tostones and finished up with lemons, tomatoes, onions,  red and green peppers  topped with Cilantro.  You will not believe this is all plant based!
A Staple in Puerto Rican comfort food!  filled with Impossible Meat and completely HP = Hecho de plantas (plant based) made with Impossible meat seasoned to perfection.
Our HP empanadas have 3 different fillings to choose from:  Impossible Meat, Bistec & Maduro (Steak & Onions w/sweet plantains) and Pizza. Choose below and enjoy!
Relleno de papa (potato ball fritter)  w/Impossible Meat
This option includes one ONE relleno.
Refreshing green salad with lettuce, tomato, onions, and shredded carrots.
Arroz con Gandules - Rice and Pigeon Peas

Loaded Fries with Beef, Cheese and Special Sauce will satisfy your cravings for something savory and satisfying. Our crispy golden fries are generously topped with juicy, seasoned beef, melted cheddar cheese, and drizzled with our signature special sauce - a mouthwatering blend of tangy mayo, zesty ketchup. Every bite is an explosion of flavor and texture that will leave you wanting more. Perfect as a snack or to share with friends, Loaded Fries with Beef, Cheese and Special Sauce is a must-try dish that you won't be able to resist.

menu_items: Interested in how Brady's can cater your next corporate party, fabulous event, third wedding, dog baptism, or Netflix & chill? Whatever. We do it all. Email us at order@bradysbakery.com, and a baker will get back to you asap. Note: do not add this item to your cart because you won’t receive anything if you do.
the BYOB variety bag - Half Dozen
individually wrapped and ready TO GO. per the cookie monster's request, here's a chance to build your own brady's (BYOB) variety bag. you can have it your way, but don't get crazy.
the BYOB variety bag - One Dozen
individually wrapped and ready TO GO. per the cookie monster's request, here's a chance to build your own brady's (BYOB) variety bag. you can have it your way, but don't get crazy.
individually wrapped and ready TO GO. our take on a classic sugar cookie. but nothing we ever do is too basic, so we've added our own sparkle to it and filled it with funfetti. who's a basic b now?
the Chocolate Chip + Sea Salt cookie

individually wrapped and ready TO GO. our best seller. just like mom used to make. and better. much better. no offense, mom. this cookie is filled to the brim with semi sweet and dark chocolate chips, a hint of cinnamon, and topped with sea salt. special requests (i.e. no salt) cannot be accommodated.
individually wrapped and ready TO GO. deliciously moist cookie filled with crushed oreo and melt-in-your-mouth creamy white chocolate. need we say more?
individually wrapped and ready TO GO. nutella filled cookie. we thought the name deemed appropriate, yes?
individually wrapped and ready TO GO. the one that started it all. it's our chocolate chip + sea salt cookie recipe, but with chopped walnuts tossed in. how nutty.
individually wrapped and ready TO GO. we want your bod. your dad bod. like, the dad bod cookie. this stud is filled with semi sweet and dark chocolate chips and hearty oats. hey, thique.
individually wrapped and ready TO GO. it’s like a snickerdoodle and a praline had a baby - and she became a southern belle. deliciously rich cinnamon ＆ sugar cookie filled with toasted pecans.
the Red Velvet + White Chocolate Chip cookie
how southern of us. deliciously velvety red cookie with a hint of cocoa and filled with creamy white chocolate. bless our hearts.
individually wrapped and ready TO GO. a delightfully soft cookie filled with fresh orange zest and poppy seeds, then dunked in a buttermilk glaze. oh, poppy indeed.

Individually wrapped and ready TO GO. Nostalgic, delicious, and crust-less peanut butter oatmeal cookie with a dollop of strawberry jelly. Made with plant-based ingredients, gluten-free flour + oats, and is completely dairy-free. perfection. This item is made in a kitchen where eggs and dairy are present.

individually wrapped and ready TO GO. camp out with our s'more inspired cookie. we've taken our popular chocolate chip + sea salt cookie and filled it with marshmallow and dark chocolate ganache, topping it with crushed graham cracker & brown sugar. gimme gimme s'more.

well hey, LA. short for lemon & almond, this light and airy cookie packs a punch with gluten free flour, fresh lemon zest, and almond meal. she also contains almost 50% less sugar than our other cookies. let the sunshine in.

individually wrapped and ready TO GO. it’s like a cinnamon roll in a cookie state of mind. this is a cinnamon cookie rolled in a brown sugar + cinnamon spread and filled with cinnamon cream cheese. it’ll make you go “woo-hoo”.

Hand-picked, organic spearmint leaves make our mint chip fresh & bright. We sprinkle in homemade chocolate chips for added crunch!

Our old fashioned vanilla is made with whole Tahitian vanilla beans. For all you vanilla lovers out there, we add a splash of Madagascar vanilla extract too!

menu_items: Add to Order for Compostable Packaging

Hi Bao Takers,
We are currently testing compostable packaging for our traditional Baos. We have been trying to move away from our sturdy packaging to more a sustainable option. However, we have been hesitant to fully roll it out because our Baos can disassemble if it is shaken too violently during delivery. It also doesn't keep the Bao as warm. Please bear with us if you receive a Bao that is messier than usual with this option. We are constantly testing and looking to improve, so we can fully transition to a more sustainable option without affecting your experience. Please let us know your experience with compostable packaging. Thank you for being a part of this!

menu_items: Add to Order for Compostable Packaging

Hi Bao Takers,
We are currently testing compostable packaging for our traditional Baos. We have been trying to move away from our sturdy packaging to more a sustainable option. However, we have been hesitant to fully roll it out because our Baos can disassemble if it is shaken too violently during delivery. It also doesn't keep the Bao as warm. Please bear with us if you receive a Bao that is messier than usual with this option. We are constantly testing and looking to improve, so we can fully transition to a more sustainable option without affecting your experience. Please let us know your experience with compostable packaging. Thank you for being a part of this!
